if (typeof Q.bumpDistrictProsperity === 'function') { Q.bumpDistrictProsperity('Aurora', 0.05); }
if (typeof Q.queueBudgetExpense === 'function') { Q.queueBudgetExpense(3, 'contract_award', 'Municipal contract award'); }
!}

Aurora's boutique fabricators and logistics brokers land the contracts.  Wealthy households across Mikasa still feel the downstream orders — and remember who signed the checks.

@cooperatives
view-if: contract_fair_chain_complete = 0
title: Local cooperatives and guilds

Cooperative workshops and guild ateliers can absorb small-batch municipal orders if we place the work where they already live.  Every site gives the local guilds a little more clout citywide.

- @coop_aurora: Aurora cooperatives
- @coop_pitts: Pitts cooperatives and Seven Families workshops
- @coop_deeps: Deeps cooperatives
- @coop_docks: Docks cooperatives and freight guilds
- @return

@coop_aurora
title: Aurora cooperatives
on-arrival: {!
contract_coop_aurora = 1;
if (typeof Q.addAsset === 'function') {
    Q.addAsset({ id: 'aurora_coop_contract_workshop', name: 'Aurora coop contract workshop', district: 'Aurora', ownerType: 'stratum', owner: 'coop', kind: 'workshop', major: false });
}
if (typeof Q.bumpDistrictProsperity === 'function') { Q.bumpDistrictProsperity('Aurora', 0.06); }
if (typeof Q.queueBudgetExpense === 'function') { Q.queueBudgetExpense(3, 'contract_award', 'Municipal contract award'); }
!}

Aurora coop yards pick up fabrication and life-support maintenance orders.  Guild brokers in other districts note that municipal business is no longer reserved for megacorp vendors.

