Pitts cooperative machine shops and syndicate-tolerant guild floors share the workload.  The Seven Families treat the contract as recognition; coop members treat it as proof the city can hire locally.

@coop_deeps
title: Deeps cooperatives
on-arrival: {!
contract_coop_deeps = 1;
if (typeof Q.addAsset === 'function') {
